model.name: Landscape Short-Sleeved Denim Shirt
model.disambiguatingDescription: This distinctive shirt made from Japanese denim features randomly placed Louis Vuitton signatures, which gradually coalesce into a Damier motif around the upper chest and shoulders. The bottom half of the shirt features a landscape in saturated colors. It can be worn with the corresponding Landscape Damier Spread Pants for a total look.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• 100% Cotton
  • Multicolor
  • Regular Fit 
  • Model wears a FR M size
  • Model measurements : chest 35.5’’ / 90 cm, height 6' 1½’’ / 187 cm
  • Made in Italy
